{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_012fuyv1SijUPFi6jhXvC6cK","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now let me create a comprehensive summary document with all the findings:\n\n## Exploration Complete - E2E Test Infrastructure Report\n\nI have successfully explored the entire E2E test infrastructure in the rng-utopia project. Here's a comprehensive overview of what exists:\n\n---\n\n### 1. **Local E2E Config** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.local.config.ts`\n\n**Purpose**: Configuration for testing against a local `solana-test-validator` with real wallet mode.\n\n**Key Settings**:\n- **Test Directory**: `./e2e` (matches `local/**/*.spec.ts`)\n- **Port**: 3002\n- **Vite Dev Server**: Auto-started with Vite on port 3002\n- **Workers**: 1 (sequential, no parallelization)\n- **Environment Variables**:\n  - `VITE_MOCK_MODE: \"false\"` (real wallet mode)\n  - `VITE_RPC_URL: \"http://127.0.0.1:8899\"` (local validator)\n  - `VITE_SOLANA_NETWORK: \"localnet\"`\n- **Timeout**: 60s per test\n- **Viewport**: 1280×1080 (Desktop Chrome)\n- **Trace**: retain-on-failure (useful for debugging failures)\n\n---\n\n### 2. **Local Smoke Test** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/smoke.spec.ts`\n\n**Purpose**: Basic smoke test verifying the app loads in real mode against the local validator.\n\n**Tests**:\n- Verifies `.rpg-title` is visible (main title renders)\n- Verifies `.rpg-wallet-icon` is visible (wallet UI renders)\n- Asserts no critical console errors\n\n---\n\n### 3. **Wallet Helpers** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/wallets.ts`\n\n**Purpose**: Deterministic wallet funding for local E2E tests.\n\n**Key Exports**:\n- **Keypairs** (deterministic from 32-byte seeds):\n  - `PLAYER_A`: seed `0xaa` repeated\n  - `PLAYER_B`: seed `0xbb` repeated\n- **Constants**:\n  - `LOCAL_RPC_URL = \"http://127.0.0.1:8899\"`\n  - `DEFAULT_AIRDROP_SOL = 10`\n\n**Functions**:\n- `fundWallet(connection, to, solAmount)`: Airdrop SOL to one wallet + confirm\n- `fundTestWallets(rpcUrl?, solAmount?)`: Fund both PLAYER_A & PLAYER_B, returns `{ playerA, playerB, connection }`\n  - Includes sanity checks to ensure balances were set correctly\n  - Call this in a `beforeAll` or global setup\n\n---\n\n### 4. **Page-Object Helpers** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/page-objects.ts`\n\n**Purpose**: Reusable coinflip page-object helpers with CSS-class-based selectors.\n\n**Key Selector Groups** (all use `.` class prefix):\n- **Lobby**: `.coinflip-lobby`, `.coinflip-main`, `.coinflip-sidebar`\n- **Create Flow**: tier selector, side selector (heads/tails), \"Create Game\" button\n- **Match Cards**: `.coinflip-match-card`, `.coinflip-match-card--own`, `.coinflip-match-card--claimable`\n- **Active Match**: `.coinflip-active-match`, `.coinflip-active-match__title--won/--lost`\n- **Result**: `.coinflip-result__outcome`, `.coinflip-result__payout`\n- **Post-Claim**: `.coinflip-active-match__post-claim`, \"Back to Lobby\" button\n- **Errors**: `.coinflip-error-toast`, `.rng-toast__message`\n\n**Action Functions**:\n- `navigateToCoinflip(page)`: Go to `/coinflip` + wait for `.coinflip-main`\n- `selectTier(page, tier)`: Click tier button + verify class\n- `selectSide(page, side: \"heads\" | \"tails\")`: Click side button + verify class\n- `createMatch(page, tier, side)`: Select tier/side + click \"Create Game\", wait for active match\n- `joinMatch(page, matchIndex?)`: Join first (or specific) joinable match, wait for active match\n- `cancelMatch(page)`: Click \"Cancel Match\" + wait for lobby\n- `claimOrSettle(page)`: Click claim/settle button in sidebar, wait for \"Back to Lobby\" button\n- `backToLobby(page)`: Click \"Back to Lobby\", wait for lobby\n\n**Wait/Assert Primitives**:\n- `waitForPhaseLabel(page, label, timeout?)`: Wait for phase text (e.g., \"Waiting...\", \"Complete\")\n- `waitForResult(page, timeout?)`: Wait for title to show won/lost, returns `\"won\" | \"lost\"`\n- `waitForLobbyMatch(page, timeout?)`: Wait for match to appear, returns Locator\n- `assertLobbyEmpty(page, timeout?)`: Assert no open match cards\n- `assertErrorToast(page, messageSubstring, timeout?)`: Assert error toast visible with text\n- `assertNoErrorToast(page)`: Assert zero error toasts\n- `getSolBalance(page, walletAddress, rpcUrl?)`: Fetch SOL balance via RPC (from page context)\n- `trackConsoleErrors(page)`: Returns `{ errors, assertClean }` — accumulate + assert no errors at end\n- `waitForText(page, text, timeout?)`: Wait for text to appear anywhere\n- `waitForLobby(page, timeout?)`: Wait for lobby to be visible\n\n**Types**:\n- `CoinSide = \"heads\" | \"tails\"`\n- `Tier = \"iron\" | \"bronze\" | \"silver\" | \"gold\" | \"platinum\" | \"diamond\"`\n\n---\n\n### 5. **On-Chain Helpers** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/on-chain.ts`\n\n**Purpose**: RPC-based assertion helpers for on-chain state queries (match PDAs, treasury, player profiles).\n\n**Key Constants**:\n- `COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID = PublicKey(CoinflipIDL.address)`\n- `PLATFORM_PROGRAM_ID = PublicKey(PlatformIDL.address)`\n- `FEE_BPS = 300` (3% platform fee)\n\n**PDA Derivation**:\n- `getMatchPda(creator)`: Seeds `[\"match\", creator.buffer]`, Coinflip program\n- `getConfigPda()`: Seeds `[\"coinflip_config\"]`, Coinflip program\n- `getPlayerProfilePda(wallet)`: Seeds `[\"player_profile\", wallet.buffer]`, Platform program\n\n**Program Instances**:\n- `getCoinflipProgram(connection)`: Read-only Coinflip program\n- `getPlatformProgram(connection)`: Read-only Platform program\n\n**Account Interfaces**:\n```typescript\ninterface MatchAccount {\n  creator: PublicKey;\n  opponent: PublicKey;\n  tier: number;\n  entryAmount: { toNumber(): number };\n  creatorSide: number; // 0=heads, 1=tails\n  phase: Record<string, object>; // { waiting: {}, locked: {}, resolved: {} }\n  result: number;\n  winner: PublicKey;\n  claimed: boolean;\n  createdAt: { toNumber(): number };\n  lockedAt: { toNumber(): number };\n  resolveDeadline: { toNumber(): number };\n  vrfRequestKey: PublicKey;\n  bump: number;\n}\n\ninterface PlayerProfileAccount {\n  authority: PublicKey;\n  totalGames: { toNumber(): number };\n  wins: { toNumber(): number };\n  totalWagered: { toNumber(): number };\n  totalWon: { toNumber(): number };\n  bump: number;\n}\n```\n\n**Fetch Helpers**:\n- `fetchMatch(connection, matchPda)`: Fetch match account, returns null if closed\n- `fetchPlayerProfile(connection, profilePda)`: Fetch player profile, returns null if not found\n- `getTreasuryAddress(connection)`: Get treasury address from config PDA\n- `getBalanceLamports(connection, address)`: Get SOL balance in lamports\n- `snapshotBalance(connection, address)`: Capture balance for delta comparison\n\n**Fee Calculation**:\n- `calculateExpectedFee(entryAmount)`: Returns `{ pool, fee, payout }` in lamports\n  - Formula: `fee = floor(pool * FEE_BPS / 10_000)` where `pool = entryAmount * 2`\n\n**Assertion Helpers**:\n- `assertMatchCreated(connection, creator, expectedTier, expectedSide)`: Assert match in waiting phase with correct setup, returns `{ matchPda, match }`\n- `assertMatchClosed(connection, matchPda)`: Assert match PDA is closed (account no longer exists)\n- `assertTreasuryFee(connection, treasury, balanceBefore, entryAmount)`: Assert treasury received expected fee delta\n- `assertPlayerProfile(connection, wallet, expected)`: Assert player profile stats match expected values\n- `assertPlayerProfileDelta(connection, wallet, before, delta)`: Assert stats changed by delta since snapshot\n- `snapshotPlayerProfile(connection, wallet)`: Snapshot stats (returns zero-stats if profile doesn't exist)\n\n---\n\n### 6. **Real Wallet Mode Config** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.real.config.ts`\n\n**Purpose**: Configuration for real wallet mode tests against Solana Devnet.\n\n**Key Settings**:\n- **Test Directory**: `./e2e` (matches `real/**/*.spec.ts`)\n- **Port**: 3001\n- **Vite Dev Server**: Auto-started on port 3001\n- **Workers**: 1 (sequential)\n- **Environment Variables**:\n  - `VITE_MOCK_MODE: \"false\"` (real wallet mode)\n  - `VITE_RPC_URL: \"https://api.devnet.solana.com\"` (Solana Devnet)\n- **Parallelization**: `fullyParallel: true` (but workers=1, so no actual parallelization)\n- **Trace**: off (devnet tests, no need to retain on failure)\n- **Screenshot**: off\n\n---\n\n### 7. **Real Mode Startup Test** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/real/startup.spec.ts`\n\n**Purpose**: Minimal real-mode tests for Devnet connectivity and wallet UI.\n\n**Custom Fixture** (`realPage`):\n- Collects console errors\n- Does NOT freeze randomness/time (needs real crypto)\n- Fails test if console errors detected\n\n**Tests**:\n1. **App loads without errors**: Navigates to `/`, verifies `.rpg-wallet-icon` visible + displays \"—\" (em dash) when disconnected\n2. **Wallet icon interaction**: Click wallet icon to trigger `connect()` → should open Unified Wallet modal or fail gracefully, app remains functional\n\n---\n\n### 8. **Visual Regression Fixture** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/fixtures.ts`\n\n**Purpose**: Shared fixture for visual regression tests (used by `test:visual`).\n\n**Custom Fixture** (`stablePage`):\n- **Deterministic Randomness**: Seeds `Math.random()` with Mulberry32 (seed=42) + `crypto.getRandomValues()`\n- **Frozen Time**: `Date.now()` frozen to 2026-01-01T00:00:00Z\n- **Animation Freeze**: Injects CSS to disable all CSS/SVG animations and transitions\n- **SVG Pause**: Calls `svg.pauseAnimations()` on all SVG elements\n- **Network Wait**: Always waits for network idle + font loading + 300ms settle time\n- **Deterministic goto()**: Wraps page.goto() to ensure all above happens after navigation\n- **Console Error Tracking**: Fails test if console errors detected\n\n---\n\n### 9. **Wallet Package Architecture** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/wallet/src/`\n\n**Top-Level Structure**:\n\n**`WalletProvider.tsx`** (Main entry point):\n- Detects mode: `VITE_MOCK_MODE === \"true\"` → MockWalletProvider, else RealWalletProvider\n- Wraps both with `ConnectionProvider` from `@solana/wallet-adapter-react`\n- RPC URL: from `VITE_RPC_URL` env, defaults to `https://api.devnet.solana.com`\n- Includes retry logic (429 handling with exponential backoff)\n\n**`context.ts`**:\n- Exports `WalletContext` (React Context with `WalletContextValue`)\n\n**`types.ts`**:\n```typescript\ninterface WalletState {\n  connected: boolean;\n  connecting: boolean;\n  address: string | null;\n  publicKey: PublicKey | null;\n}\n\ninterface WalletContextValue extends WalletState {\n  connect: () => Promise<void>;\n  disconnect: () => Promise<void>;\n  sendTransaction: (transaction: Transaction) => Promise<string>;\n  signMessage: (message: Uint8Array) => Promise<Uint8Array>;\n  isMock?: boolean;\n  getBalance?: () => number; // mock only\n  getBalanceLamports?: () => number; // mock only\n  updateBalance?: (deltaLamports: number) => void; // mock only\n}\n```\n\n**`mock/MockWalletProvider.tsx`**:\n- Provides in-memory wallet with mock balance state\n- Config options:\n  - `initialBalance`: in SOL (default 1000)\n  - `autoConnect`: bool (default false)\n  - `simulatedLatency`: ms (default 500)\n  - `persistState`: bool (default true, uses localStorage)\n- Implements: `connect()`, `disconnect()`, `sendTransaction()`, `signMessage()`\n- Also exposes: `getBalance()`, `getBalanceLamports()`, `updateBalance(deltaLamports)`\n- Mock transactions have 5% simulated failure rate\n\n**`mock/MockWalletState.ts`**:\n- Helper utilities for mock wallet\n- Exports: `MockConfig`, `createMockKeypair()`, `loadPersistedState()`, `persistState()`, `clearPersistedState()`, `generateMockSignature()`, `delay()`, `solToLamports()`, `lamportsToSol()`, `getPublicKeyFromAddress()`\n\n**`real/RealWalletProvider.tsx`**:\n- Uses `@solana/wallet-adapter-react` + `@jup-ag/wallet-adapter` (Unified Wallet)\n- `WalletBridge` component: reads from adapter hooks → maps to `WalletContextValue` → provides via `WalletContext`\n- `connect()`: Opens Unified Wallet modal or reconnects if wallet already selected\n- Detects cluster from `VITE_SOLANA_NETWORK` env (defaults to devnet)\n\n**`test/TestWalletProvider.tsx`** (NEW - For E2E tests):\n```typescript\ninterface TestWalletProviderProps {\n  children: ReactNode;\n  keypair: Keypair;\n  rpcUrl?: string; // default: http://127.0.0.1:8899\n  autoConnect?: boolean; // default: true\n}\n```\n- Signs real transactions with injected Keypair\n- Validates account exists on connect\n- **Does NOT use browser extension** — keypair passed directly\n- `sendTransaction()`: Sets feePayer + calls `sendAndConfirmTransaction()`\n- `signMessage()`: Returns deterministic signature from keypair's secret key (first 64 bytes)\n- Use in local E2E tests where you have the keypair seed\n\n---\n\n### 10. **Test Commands** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/package.json`\n\n```json\n\"test:visual\": \"playwright test\",\n\"test:visual:update\": \"playwright test --update-snapshots\",\n\"test:real\": \"playwright test --config playwright.real.config.ts\",\n\"test:e2e:local\": \"playwright test --config playwright.local.config.ts\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Summary: Three Testing Modes\n\n| **Mode** | **Config** | **Wallet** | **RPC** | **Purpose** |\n|----------|-----------|-----------|---------|------------|\n| **Local E2E** | `playwright.local.config.ts` | TestWalletProvider + deterministic keypairs | `http://127.0.0.1:8899` (local validator) | Full integration tests with real on-chain execution, reproducible state |\n| **Real (Devnet)** | `playwright.real.config.ts` | @solana/wallet-adapter-react (Unified Wallet) | `https://api.devnet.solana.com` | Real wallet modal testing (headless-friendly) |\n| **Visual** | implicit (fixtures.ts) | Mock or Real (depends on env) | Varies | Snapshot regression testing with deterministic randomness/time |\n\n---\n\n## Key Insights\n\n1. **Deterministic Testing**: Local E2E uses fixed seed keypairs (PLAYER_A, PLAYER_B) for reproducible test runs\n2. **On-Chain Assertions**: Comprehensive PDA-based helpers for validating match state, treasury fees, and player profiles\n3. **Dual Wallet Modes**:\n   - **Mock Mode**: For UI-only testing, fast, deterministic\n   - **Real Mode**: For actual wallet + RPC interaction\n   - **Test Mode** (TestWalletProvider): For E2E with real transactions but no browser extension needed\n4. **Page Objects**: CSS-class-based selectors matching coinflip component markup — reusable across tests\n5. **Fixture Pattern**: Custom Playwright fixtures (`stablePage`, `realPage`) for determinism and error tracking\n6. **Visual Regressions**: Fully deterministic snapshot testing via seeded randomness, frozen time, and animation freezing\n\nAll files are located under `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/` with these key paths:\n- **E2E configs**: `apps/platform/playwright.*.config.ts`\n- **E2E tests**: `apps/platform/e2e/{local,real}/`\n- **E2E helpers**: `apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/`\n- **Wallet package**: `packages/wallet/src/`"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a1051cd33f2ca5e3d (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 57052\ntool_uses: 22\nduration_ms: 63815</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"610aad72-d9dc-40e7-807d-09548f27772e","uuid":"72cfbf49-31a7-4136-9010-9ce9304dc493","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Explore the existing E2E test infrastructure in the rng-utopia project. I need to understand:\n\n1. The local E2E config: `apps/platform/playwright.local.config.ts`\n2. The existing smoke spec: `apps/platform/e2e/local/smoke.spec.ts`\n3. The wallet helpers: `apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/wallets.ts`\n4. The page-object helpers: `apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/page-objects.ts`\n5. The on-chain helpers: `apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/on-chain.ts`\n6. The existing real-mode config or any existing dual-context patterns: check `apps/platform/playwright.real.config.ts` and `apps/platform/e2e/real/`\n7. The TestWalletProvider from the wallet package: check `packages/wallet/src/` for TestWalletProvider or test wallet context\n\nRead all these files and report their full contents. The base path is `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/`.","agentId":"a1051cd33f2ca5e3d","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! Now let me create a comprehensive summary document with all the findings:\n\n## Exploration Complete - E2E Test Infrastructure Report\n\nI have successfully explored the entire E2E test infrastructure in the rng-utopia project. Here's a comprehensive overview of what exists:\n\n---\n\n### 1. **Local E2E Config** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.local.config.ts`\n\n**Purpose**: Configuration for testing against a local `solana-test-validator` with real wallet mode.\n\n**Key Settings**:\n- **Test Directory**: `./e2e` (matches `local/**/*.spec.ts`)\n- **Port**: 3002\n- **Vite Dev Server**: Auto-started with Vite on port 3002\n- **Workers**: 1 (sequential, no parallelization)\n- **Environment Variables**:\n  - `VITE_MOCK_MODE: \"false\"` (real wallet mode)\n  - `VITE_RPC_URL: \"http://127.0.0.1:8899\"` (local validator)\n  - `VITE_SOLANA_NETWORK: \"localnet\"`\n- **Timeout**: 60s per test\n- **Viewport**: 1280×1080 (Desktop Chrome)\n- **Trace**: retain-on-failure (useful for debugging failures)\n\n---\n\n### 2. **Local Smoke Test** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/smoke.spec.ts`\n\n**Purpose**: Basic smoke test verifying the app loads in real mode against the local validator.\n\n**Tests**:\n- Verifies `.rpg-title` is visible (main title renders)\n- Verifies `.rpg-wallet-icon` is visible (wallet UI renders)\n- Asserts no critical console errors\n\n---\n\n### 3. **Wallet Helpers** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/wallets.ts`\n\n**Purpose**: Deterministic wallet funding for local E2E tests.\n\n**Key Exports**:\n- **Keypairs** (deterministic from 32-byte seeds):\n  - `PLAYER_A`: seed `0xaa` repeated\n  - `PLAYER_B`: seed `0xbb` repeated\n- **Constants**:\n  - `LOCAL_RPC_URL = \"http://127.0.0.1:8899\"`\n  - `DEFAULT_AIRDROP_SOL = 10`\n\n**Functions**:\n- `fundWallet(connection, to, solAmount)`: Airdrop SOL to one wallet + confirm\n- `fundTestWallets(rpcUrl?, solAmount?)`: Fund both PLAYER_A & PLAYER_B, returns `{ playerA, playerB, connection }`\n  - Includes sanity checks to ensure balances were set correctly\n  - Call this in a `beforeAll` or global setup\n\n---\n\n### 4. **Page-Object Helpers** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/page-objects.ts`\n\n**Purpose**: Reusable coinflip page-object helpers with CSS-class-based selectors.\n\n**Key Selector Groups** (all use `.` class prefix):\n- **Lobby**: `.coinflip-lobby`, `.coinflip-main`, `.coinflip-sidebar`\n- **Create Flow**: tier selector, side selector (heads/tails), \"Create Game\" button\n- **Match Cards**: `.coinflip-match-card`, `.coinflip-match-card--own`, `.coinflip-match-card--claimable`\n- **Active Match**: `.coinflip-active-match`, `.coinflip-active-match__title--won/--lost`\n- **Result**: `.coinflip-result__outcome`, `.coinflip-result__payout`\n- **Post-Claim**: `.coinflip-active-match__post-claim`, \"Back to Lobby\" button\n- **Errors**: `.coinflip-error-toast`, `.rng-toast__message`\n\n**Action Functions**:\n- `navigateToCoinflip(page)`: Go to `/coinflip` + wait for `.coinflip-main`\n- `selectTier(page, tier)`: Click tier button + verify class\n- `selectSide(page, side: \"heads\" | \"tails\")`: Click side button + verify class\n- `createMatch(page, tier, side)`: Select tier/side + click \"Create Game\", wait for active match\n- `joinMatch(page, matchIndex?)`: Join first (or specific) joinable match, wait for active match\n- `cancelMatch(page)`: Click \"Cancel Match\" + wait for lobby\n- `claimOrSettle(page)`: Click claim/settle button in sidebar, wait for \"Back to Lobby\" button\n- `backToLobby(page)`: Click \"Back to Lobby\", wait for lobby\n\n**Wait/Assert Primitives**:\n- `waitForPhaseLabel(page, label, timeout?)`: Wait for phase text (e.g., \"Waiting...\", \"Complete\")\n- `waitForResult(page, timeout?)`: Wait for title to show won/lost, returns `\"won\" | \"lost\"`\n- `waitForLobbyMatch(page, timeout?)`: Wait for match to appear, returns Locator\n- `assertLobbyEmpty(page, timeout?)`: Assert no open match cards\n- `assertErrorToast(page, messageSubstring, timeout?)`: Assert error toast visible with text\n- `assertNoErrorToast(page)`: Assert zero error toasts\n- `getSolBalance(page, walletAddress, rpcUrl?)`: Fetch SOL balance via RPC (from page context)\n- `trackConsoleErrors(page)`: Returns `{ errors, assertClean }` — accumulate + assert no errors at end\n- `waitForText(page, text, timeout?)`: Wait for text to appear anywhere\n- `waitForLobby(page, timeout?)`: Wait for lobby to be visible\n\n**Types**:\n- `CoinSide = \"heads\" | \"tails\"`\n- `Tier = \"iron\" | \"bronze\" | \"silver\" | \"gold\" | \"platinum\" | \"diamond\"`\n\n---\n\n### 5. **On-Chain Helpers** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/on-chain.ts`\n\n**Purpose**: RPC-based assertion helpers for on-chain state queries (match PDAs, treasury, player profiles).\n\n**Key Constants**:\n- `COINFLIP_PROGRAM_ID = PublicKey(CoinflipIDL.address)`\n- `PLATFORM_PROGRAM_ID = PublicKey(PlatformIDL.address)`\n- `FEE_BPS = 300` (3% platform fee)\n\n**PDA Derivation**:\n- `getMatchPda(creator)`: Seeds `[\"match\", creator.buffer]`, Coinflip program\n- `getConfigPda()`: Seeds `[\"coinflip_config\"]`, Coinflip program\n- `getPlayerProfilePda(wallet)`: Seeds `[\"player_profile\", wallet.buffer]`, Platform program\n\n**Program Instances**:\n- `getCoinflipProgram(connection)`: Read-only Coinflip program\n- `getPlatformProgram(connection)`: Read-only Platform program\n\n**Account Interfaces**:\n```typescript\ninterface MatchAccount {\n  creator: PublicKey;\n  opponent: PublicKey;\n  tier: number;\n  entryAmount: { toNumber(): number };\n  creatorSide: number; // 0=heads, 1=tails\n  phase: Record<string, object>; // { waiting: {}, locked: {}, resolved: {} }\n  result: number;\n  winner: PublicKey;\n  claimed: boolean;\n  createdAt: { toNumber(): number };\n  lockedAt: { toNumber(): number };\n  resolveDeadline: { toNumber(): number };\n  vrfRequestKey: PublicKey;\n  bump: number;\n}\n\ninterface PlayerProfileAccount {\n  authority: PublicKey;\n  totalGames: { toNumber(): number };\n  wins: { toNumber(): number };\n  totalWagered: { toNumber(): number };\n  totalWon: { toNumber(): number };\n  bump: number;\n}\n```\n\n**Fetch Helpers**:\n- `fetchMatch(connection, matchPda)`: Fetch match account, returns null if closed\n- `fetchPlayerProfile(connection, profilePda)`: Fetch player profile, returns null if not found\n- `getTreasuryAddress(connection)`: Get treasury address from config PDA\n- `getBalanceLamports(connection, address)`: Get SOL balance in lamports\n- `snapshotBalance(connection, address)`: Capture balance for delta comparison\n\n**Fee Calculation**:\n- `calculateExpectedFee(entryAmount)`: Returns `{ pool, fee, payout }` in lamports\n  - Formula: `fee = floor(pool * FEE_BPS / 10_000)` where `pool = entryAmount * 2`\n\n**Assertion Helpers**:\n- `assertMatchCreated(connection, creator, expectedTier, expectedSide)`: Assert match in waiting phase with correct setup, returns `{ matchPda, match }`\n- `assertMatchClosed(connection, matchPda)`: Assert match PDA is closed (account no longer exists)\n- `assertTreasuryFee(connection, treasury, balanceBefore, entryAmount)`: Assert treasury received expected fee delta\n- `assertPlayerProfile(connection, wallet, expected)`: Assert player profile stats match expected values\n- `assertPlayerProfileDelta(connection, wallet, before, delta)`: Assert stats changed by delta since snapshot\n- `snapshotPlayerProfile(connection, wallet)`: Snapshot stats (returns zero-stats if profile doesn't exist)\n\n---\n\n### 6. **Real Wallet Mode Config** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/playwright.real.config.ts`\n\n**Purpose**: Configuration for real wallet mode tests against Solana Devnet.\n\n**Key Settings**:\n- **Test Directory**: `./e2e` (matches `real/**/*.spec.ts`)\n- **Port**: 3001\n- **Vite Dev Server**: Auto-started on port 3001\n- **Workers**: 1 (sequential)\n- **Environment Variables**:\n  - `VITE_MOCK_MODE: \"false\"` (real wallet mode)\n  - `VITE_RPC_URL: \"https://api.devnet.solana.com\"` (Solana Devnet)\n- **Parallelization**: `fullyParallel: true` (but workers=1, so no actual parallelization)\n- **Trace**: off (devnet tests, no need to retain on failure)\n- **Screenshot**: off\n\n---\n\n### 7. **Real Mode Startup Test** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/real/startup.spec.ts`\n\n**Purpose**: Minimal real-mode tests for Devnet connectivity and wallet UI.\n\n**Custom Fixture** (`realPage`):\n- Collects console errors\n- Does NOT freeze randomness/time (needs real crypto)\n- Fails test if console errors detected\n\n**Tests**:\n1. **App loads without errors**: Navigates to `/`, verifies `.rpg-wallet-icon` visible + displays \"—\" (em dash) when disconnected\n2. **Wallet icon interaction**: Click wallet icon to trigger `connect()` → should open Unified Wallet modal or fail gracefully, app remains functional\n\n---\n\n### 8. **Visual Regression Fixture** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/e2e/fixtures.ts`\n\n**Purpose**: Shared fixture for visual regression tests (used by `test:visual`).\n\n**Custom Fixture** (`stablePage`):\n- **Deterministic Randomness**: Seeds `Math.random()` with Mulberry32 (seed=42) + `crypto.getRandomValues()`\n- **Frozen Time**: `Date.now()` frozen to 2026-01-01T00:00:00Z\n- **Animation Freeze**: Injects CSS to disable all CSS/SVG animations and transitions\n- **SVG Pause**: Calls `svg.pauseAnimations()` on all SVG elements\n- **Network Wait**: Always waits for network idle + font loading + 300ms settle time\n- **Deterministic goto()**: Wraps page.goto() to ensure all above happens after navigation\n- **Console Error Tracking**: Fails test if console errors detected\n\n---\n\n### 9. **Wallet Package Architecture** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/packages/wallet/src/`\n\n**Top-Level Structure**:\n\n**`WalletProvider.tsx`** (Main entry point):\n- Detects mode: `VITE_MOCK_MODE === \"true\"` → MockWalletProvider, else RealWalletProvider\n- Wraps both with `ConnectionProvider` from `@solana/wallet-adapter-react`\n- RPC URL: from `VITE_RPC_URL` env, defaults to `https://api.devnet.solana.com`\n- Includes retry logic (429 handling with exponential backoff)\n\n**`context.ts`**:\n- Exports `WalletContext` (React Context with `WalletContextValue`)\n\n**`types.ts`**:\n```typescript\ninterface WalletState {\n  connected: boolean;\n  connecting: boolean;\n  address: string | null;\n  publicKey: PublicKey | null;\n}\n\ninterface WalletContextValue extends WalletState {\n  connect: () => Promise<void>;\n  disconnect: () => Promise<void>;\n  sendTransaction: (transaction: Transaction) => Promise<string>;\n  signMessage: (message: Uint8Array) => Promise<Uint8Array>;\n  isMock?: boolean;\n  getBalance?: () => number; // mock only\n  getBalanceLamports?: () => number; // mock only\n  updateBalance?: (deltaLamports: number) => void; // mock only\n}\n```\n\n**`mock/MockWalletProvider.tsx`**:\n- Provides in-memory wallet with mock balance state\n- Config options:\n  - `initialBalance`: in SOL (default 1000)\n  - `autoConnect`: bool (default false)\n  - `simulatedLatency`: ms (default 500)\n  - `persistState`: bool (default true, uses localStorage)\n- Implements: `connect()`, `disconnect()`, `sendTransaction()`, `signMessage()`\n- Also exposes: `getBalance()`, `getBalanceLamports()`, `updateBalance(deltaLamports)`\n- Mock transactions have 5% simulated failure rate\n\n**`mock/MockWalletState.ts`**:\n- Helper utilities for mock wallet\n- Exports: `MockConfig`, `createMockKeypair()`, `loadPersistedState()`, `persistState()`, `clearPersistedState()`, `generateMockSignature()`, `delay()`, `solToLamports()`, `lamportsToSol()`, `getPublicKeyFromAddress()`\n\n**`real/RealWalletProvider.tsx`**:\n- Uses `@solana/wallet-adapter-react` + `@jup-ag/wallet-adapter` (Unified Wallet)\n- `WalletBridge` component: reads from adapter hooks → maps to `WalletContextValue` → provides via `WalletContext`\n- `connect()`: Opens Unified Wallet modal or reconnects if wallet already selected\n- Detects cluster from `VITE_SOLANA_NETWORK` env (defaults to devnet)\n\n**`test/TestWalletProvider.tsx`** (NEW - For E2E tests):\n```typescript\ninterface TestWalletProviderProps {\n  children: ReactNode;\n  keypair: Keypair;\n  rpcUrl?: string; // default: http://127.0.0.1:8899\n  autoConnect?: boolean; // default: true\n}\n```\n- Signs real transactions with injected Keypair\n- Validates account exists on connect\n- **Does NOT use browser extension** — keypair passed directly\n- `sendTransaction()`: Sets feePayer + calls `sendAndConfirmTransaction()`\n- `signMessage()`: Returns deterministic signature from keypair's secret key (first 64 bytes)\n- Use in local E2E tests where you have the keypair seed\n\n---\n\n### 10. **Test Commands** — `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/package.json`\n\n```json\n\"test:visual\": \"playwright test\",\n\"test:visual:update\": \"playwright test --update-snapshots\",\n\"test:real\": \"playwright test --config playwright.real.config.ts\",\n\"test:e2e:local\": \"playwright test --config playwright.local.config.ts\"\n```\n\n---\n\n## Summary: Three Testing Modes\n\n| **Mode** | **Config** | **Wallet** | **RPC** | **Purpose** |\n|----------|-----------|-----------|---------|------------|\n| **Local E2E** | `playwright.local.config.ts` | TestWalletProvider + deterministic keypairs | `http://127.0.0.1:8899` (local validator) | Full integration tests with real on-chain execution, reproducible state |\n| **Real (Devnet)** | `playwright.real.config.ts` | @solana/wallet-adapter-react (Unified Wallet) | `https://api.devnet.solana.com` | Real wallet modal testing (headless-friendly) |\n| **Visual** | implicit (fixtures.ts) | Mock or Real (depends on env) | Varies | Snapshot regression testing with deterministic randomness/time |\n\n---\n\n## Key Insights\n\n1. **Deterministic Testing**: Local E2E uses fixed seed keypairs (PLAYER_A, PLAYER_B) for reproducible test runs\n2. **On-Chain Assertions**: Comprehensive PDA-based helpers for validating match state, treasury fees, and player profiles\n3. **Dual Wallet Modes**:\n   - **Mock Mode**: For UI-only testing, fast, deterministic\n   - **Real Mode**: For actual wallet + RPC interaction\n   - **Test Mode** (TestWalletProvider): For E2E with real transactions but no browser extension needed\n4. **Page Objects**: CSS-class-based selectors matching coinflip component markup — reusable across tests\n5. **Fixture Pattern**: Custom Playwright fixtures (`stablePage`, `realPage`) for determinism and error tracking\n6. **Visual Regressions**: Fully deterministic snapshot testing via seeded randomness, frozen time, and animation freezing\n\nAll files are located under `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/` with these key paths:\n- **E2E configs**: `apps/platform/playwright.*.config.ts`\n- **E2E tests**: `apps/platform/e2e/{local,real}/`\n- **E2E helpers**: `apps/platform/e2e/local/helpers/`\n- **Wallet package**: `packages/wallet/src/`"}],"totalDurationMs":63815,"totalTokens":57052,"totalToolUseCount":22,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":513,"cache_read_input_tokens":51850,"o